queries.nl_query: show all temas with players whoare also second baseman
queries.sql_query: SELECT DISTINCT team.* FROM team JOIN player ON team.teamID = player.teamID WHERE player.positions LIKE '%2B%' LIMIT 100;
queries.formatted_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT team.*
FROM team
JOIN player ON team.teamID = player.teamID
WHERE player.positions LIKE '%2B%'
LIMIT 100;

queries.nl_query: show all teams that have a logo
queries.sql_query: SELECT * FROM team WHERE logo IS NOT NULL LIMIT 100

SELECT *
FROM team
WHERE logo IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 100
